dc_description_s: These data layers represent zoning in Jefferson county in 2019 and 2018. The following features and the table are included: 'Jefferson_GENERAL_2019, 'Jefferson_SHORELAND_2018” and 'JEFFERSON_GENERAL_ZONING_CODES_2019'. For General: [This file contains the polygons for all parcels in Jefferson County and the data related to the zoning designation for all tax parcels.] For Shoreland: [Indicators for developement restrictions developed by using a 1000 foot buffer of DNR Hydro Polygons and 300 foot buffer on linear highwater mark from waterway DNR Hydro Stream Bank data set. Also included is the 100 Year Flood Risk developed by FEMA DFirm dataset 2015.]
